#
# Test cases created during the EDK II adoption of uncrustify.
#
# Note: Some of these tests can likely move to more generic areas such
#       the C language tests. They are kept here to prevent conflicts
#       from syncing with the upstream and to easily identify the tests
#       so they can be filtered appropriately in the future.
#
# Range: 00000 - 09999
# test.name  config.file  input.file

# pre-processor

00000  edk2.cfg                             edk2/preproc-string-comment.c
00001  edk2.cfg                             edk2/struct-init-indent.c
00002  edk2.cfg                             edk2/multi-line-debug-code-macro-call.c
